highlights.text: “反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1512 days straight.
MC 張天賦 has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “東邪” is the highest at #13.

“I’ll Be There” by Jin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 108 spots at #82.
